            frontends,
            but
            I&#x2019;m sure good Whisper UI frontends exist.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="split-card-grid mt-lg">
      <div class="large">
        <h2 id="font-editors" class="title">Font Editors</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://fontforge.org/en-US/">FontForge</a></li>
