    <div class="split-card-grid mt-lg">
      <div class="large">
        <h2 id="programming" class="title">Programming</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/go-gitea/gitea">gitea</a>: Self-hosted GitHub</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.postman.com/">Postman</a>: Backend API testing and request-making GUI</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.vmware.com/products/workstation-player.html">VMware Workstation Player</a>: Free
            virtual
            machine runner</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/">Docker Desktop</a>: GUI frontend for Docker</li>
          <li><a href="https://rufus.ie/en/">Rufus</a>: GUI tool for creating bootable USB drives.</li>
          <li><a href="https://openhardwaremonitor.org/">OpenHardwareMonitor</a>: Tool which monitors chip temperatures,
            voltages, and more.</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.cpuid.com/softwares/cpu-z.html">CPU-Z</a>: View information about some of the
